- You mean the tires I slashed?

00:15.040 --> 00:20.720
That's my book. The reason I have it
is because Matthew has autism.

00:20.920 --> 00:23.360
That doesn't mean Vic and his guys
didn't steal drugs.

00:23.520 --> 00:25.880
- But without evidence...
- I saw them pocket cocaine.

00:26.080 --> 00:29.480
