my people are trying to cover up.

00:40.080 --> 00:43.960
- Dirty cops?
- You'll see it gets publicity.

00:44.120 --> 00:48.280
Don't worry, David. I'll make sure
they spell your name right.

00:51.120 --> 00:55.160
You have an open warrant
for your arrest. Don't worry.

00:55.880 --> 00:58.400
Your boyfriend'll lock up.
Won't you, officer?

