01:36.920 --> 01:38.280
Julien!

01:39.280 --> 01:41.520
Don't gun it!
Too many people!

01:41.720 --> 01:44.360
On the wrong side of the road again!
There's a vehicle!

01:44.520 --> 01:45.800
That was nearly a collision!

01:49.720 --> 01:52.920
Farmington cops investigated
for stealing drugs?

01:53.080 --> 01:56.080
The chief dunked my balls like a couple
of doughnuts in his coffee.

01:56.240 --> 01:59.440
- You have any idea how this got out?
- Yeah! You leaked it!

01:59.880 --> 02:01.760
- Me?
- You come across like a crusading...

02:01.920 --> 02:04.240
...cop bucking the system.
- We're all hurt.

02:04.400 --> 02:07.520
No one succeeds in this department
by being anti-cop.

02:07.720 --> 02:10.039
I'm anti-criminal.
Even if they're wearing a badge.

02:10.199 --> 02:12.600
I must've missed that quote
in the paper.

02:12.760 --> 02:15.440
What're you gonna do about the
Strike Team? Suspend them?

02:15.640 --> 02:18.840
- Innocent until proven guilty.
- Can't have them running the streets...

02:19.000 --> 02:22.000
...with these charges pending.
- And we can't suspend officers...

02:22.160 --> 02:25.840
...without due process. Reassign
the team to the general detective pool.

02:26.040 --> 02:29.480
- Stick them with different partners.
- In the meantime, I'll see if I can...

02:29.640 --> 02:32.000
...figure out who leaked this.
- Don't bother.

02:32.160 --> 02:35.080
Do you wanna pack your things
now or would you like a few days?

02:35.240 --> 02:39.160
Firing the one cop who actually cares
about cleaning up the department.

02:39.320 --> 02:41.600
I wonder how the chief would like
that headline.

02:42.920 --> 02:45.280
You got it all figured out,
don't you?

02:53.880 --> 02:56.440
- Howdy, partner.
- Slumming with us ordinary detectives.

02:56.640 --> 02:58.720
Don't get too excited.
It's just temporary.

02:58.880 --> 03:00.400
Promises, promises.

03:00.600 --> 03:02.760
Looks like we're running
together today.

03:04.320 --> 03:06.640
- Yeah.
- There's traffic up ahead.

03:06.800 --> 03:08.880
- He's trying to get...
- Northbound, over.

03:09.040 --> 03:11.440
It's coming our way.
Block this intersection.

03:16.480 --> 03:19.480
- When we're clear, cross the street.
- Shouldn't I follow?

03:19.640 --> 03:23.480
