to Shane Vendrell about all day?

03:43.040 --> 03:44.440
It's good to shake things up.

03:44.600 --> 03:47.280
I don't wanna shake things up.
I want my partner back.

03:47.440 --> 03:51.160
Aren't you sweet? Well, absence
makes the heart grow fonder.

03:53.040 --> 03:55.120
