of an emotional release sex.

13:09.400 --> 13:11.600
- You're kidding, right?
- What?

13:12.040 --> 13:17.280
You've never covered some homicide
and gone back later for a statement?

13:18.080 --> 13:22.080
This one's been hanging on the vine
for a year, man. She is ripe.

13:27.800 --> 13:31.120
- Get out of here! She's with me now.
- Just give me two minutes, man.

13:31.280 --> 13:35.040
